The paper discusses the design, training, and testing of deep neural networks, which are commonly used in pattern recognition, computer vision, and artificial intelligence research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also discusses the technical aspects of deep learning, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
